author: coar
msg: Adding colours for the links so the text will be visible
in case the end-user has his default set to white-on-black
or something like that.  Also changing the background colour
to use #rrggbb syntax - not all browsers are mnemonic-aware.

author: coar
msg: Changed colours from mnemonics to #rrggbb syntax, since some
older browsers (e.g., Mozilla 1.1) don't know the names yet.
Submitted by:	Comments from Marc Slemko, Brian Behlendorf
